                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9420" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1415</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1558 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">债劫难逃，能否起死回生：中天金融破产重整之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Debt disaster is difficult to escape, Can It Be Brought Back to Life: The Path of Zhongtian Finance’s Bankruptcy and Restructuring</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">韩楠，吕伟聪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕山大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中天金融集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破产重整；债务危机；中天金融；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Bankruptcy reorganization；Debt crisis；Zhongtian Finance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中天金融作为贵州省首家上市公司，曾多次入选中国500强企业。然而，由于大规模扩张，公司陷入巨额亏损，资不抵债。2023年6月30日，中天金融股票连续二十个交易日收盘价均低于1元/股，黯然退出A股市场。从此，公司踏上了破产重整之路。本案例以中天金融债务危机的爆发为切入点，回顾了其从创立到崛起再到多元化发展的历程，详细地描述了中天金融从地产迈向金融领域，却在外部环境和内部经营政策的影响下深陷债务泥潭，踏上破产重整的征途。本案例旨在引导学生掌握财务预警的方法，探究企业陷入债务危机的原因，理解破产重整的定义、破产重整的价值及破产重整的措施，启发学生从多角度思考企业选择破产重整化债的原因，为其他企业防范和应对债务危机提供建议。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the first listed company in Guizhou Province, Zhongtian Finance has been selected multiple times as one of the top 500 Chinese enterprises. However, due to large-scale expansion, the company suffered huge losses and was unable to repay its debts. On June 30, 2023, Zhongtian Finance&#39;s stock closed below 1 yuan per share for twenty consecutive trading days, and withdrew from the A-share market in disappointment. From then on, the company embarked on the path of bankruptcy reorganization. This case takes the outbreak of Zhongtian Finance&#39;s debt crisis as the starting point, reviews its process from establishment to rise and then to diversified development, and describes in detail its transition from real estate to the financial field, but it is deeply mired in debt under the influence of external environment and internal policies, and embarks on the process of bankruptcy reorganization. The purpose of this case is to guide students to master the methods of financial warning, explore the reasons why companies fall into debt crises, understand the definition, value, and measures of bankruptcy reorganization, inspire students to think from multiple perspectives about the reasons why companies choose bankruptcy reorganization, and provide suggestions for other companies to prevent and respond to debt crises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险管理理论；财务预警基本方法；债务危机定义及动因；破产重整；破产和解；破产清算；破产重整价值；破产重整模式；债务危机防范及应对思路；</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
